gets me to thinking...

> I used a pair of 4x9" speakers installed into the cover that hides the 
> hatch springs. They sound great, and you can always hear them 
> regardless of how heavily loaded the westy gets. 4x9's may be a bit 
> harder to find, but they are also a lot easier to find places to 
